Package: ScIsoX
Title: Single-Cell Hierarchical Tensor (SCHT) Creation Pipeline and Transcriptomic Complexity Analysis in R
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-04-22
Authors@R: c(
    person("Siyuan", "Wu", email = "thaddeus.wu@jcu.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ulf", "Schmitz", role = "aut"))
Description: This package enables comprehensive analysis of transcriptomic complexity
    at single-cell resolution. It provides tools for quality control, normalisation, 
    and creation of Single-Cell Hierarchical Tensor (SCHT) structures, which facilitate 
    detailed investigation of transcriptomic complexity across different cell types. 
    The package includes functions for calculating seven core complexity metrics, visualising 
    those metrics, and exploring cell type-specific isoform expression pattern. 
